name: Tamtel Skreej (V)
Lore: 'Gambler. Lando Calrissian posed as a guard for Jabba in order to spy on the Hutt. Feared that he would be recognized by some of Jabba''s companions.',
Text: 'Deploys only to a Tatooine site as an Undercover spy. Once during each control phase, if Undercover, may relocate your character at a related site to Lando''s site (for free). Once per game, may deploy Vibro-Ax on Lando from Reserve Deck for free; reshuffle.',
